<br>
The bard spell is <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3362&amp;source=Live"> Rizlona's Call of Flame</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
<br>
Ya, about the cleric stacking. I guess stacking is not in the spell data info. But, I know they stack because we gave a mage spell haste focus item to a cleric who had the buff up and the displayed casting time was 25% of the original, which means at least these two effects stack. But, cannot quite guess how to test damage focus testing as easily. I would guess this sort of stacking is like melee haste stacking. Spell haste does not stack with spell haste but item and bard haste does.<br>
<br>
Oh and there is another very weird set of focus effects:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3084&amp;source=Live">Inferno of Solusek</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3081&amp;source=Live">Combustion of Ro</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3085&amp;source=Live">Burning Blaze</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3082&amp;source=Live">Venom of the Tainted</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3082&amp;source=Live">Torbas' Vengeance</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3086&amp;source=Live">Chaos Storm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3080&amp;source=Live">Wrath of the Ages</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
They went in nearly at the last minute and seem to double the damage of one low level nuke for each priest and int caster class.<br>
<br>
And, here is some pure conjecture for ya. Maybe <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3550&amp;source=Live">Innoruuk's Irony</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> and <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3549&amp;source=Live">Innoruuk's Sarcasm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> will end up being the missing reanimation focus effects. They seem to have the look of the other focus effects with an unknown part in place of the effect they modify by a percent. I suppose it is more likely that they are some sort of focus effect that modifies the poison counter in some way. <p>-- <br>
